  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8144345/" class="title-link">见微知著</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8144345"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/shaqingqing/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1385730-68.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shaqingqing/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">BBpanda</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-10-26"
      class="main-meta">2016-10-26 09:10:00</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8144345_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  1966年6月18日，中共中央办公厅（中办）宣布成立秘书局，撤销原来的机要室、秘书室及书记处研究室。原中办翻译组也随之不复存在。翻译组组长、长期担任中国最高领导人俄语翻译的阎明复奉命搬出中南海，转而迎来了长达近十年遭审查、关押的蹉跎岁月。2015年，84岁高龄的阎明复终...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">13有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8144345_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8144345_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
